Introduction of the concept of smart youth work. Development of competences for high quality use of digital tools in youth work.Objectives/eesmärkid:  The student uses digital tools for quality work with young people.Learning outcomes/õpiväljund:  The student:  - understands the most important approaches to using technology in education, including informal learning;  - understands the formation and development of smart youth work in Estonia and the European Union;  - describes the technologies that are used in developing work with young people;  - analyses digital technologies used to develop activities in work with young people, to consider dangers of the Internet.
